    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>''There used to be a saying in New York, 'I should live so long.'''</p>
        <p>WILLIAM J. RONAN, the first chairman of the Metropolitan Transportation Authority, discussing the on-and-off plans for a Second Avenue subway, first announced in 1929. [B4]</p>
